00:01:14.650 --> 00:01:16.390 align:middle line:90%
of public policy.

00:01:16.390 --> 00:01:17.954 align:middle line:90%
But this really works.

00:01:17.954 --> 00:01:24.730 align:middle line:90%
[CHEERING]

00:01:24.730 --> 00:01:28.030 align:middle line:84%
>> But are they really running
