00:01:36.490 --> 00:01:38.200 align:middle line:90%
screening programs.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:41.260 align:middle line:84%
Their work is throwing the very
definition of the word cancer

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:46.510 align:middle line:84%
