00:02:12.226 --> 00:02:24.060 align:middle line:90%


00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:26.730 align:middle line:84%
>> For a long time, I thought
that breast screening was

00:02:26.730 --> 00:02:30.450 align:middle line:84%
a good thing until the day my
mother's mammogram revealed

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:33.120 align:middle line:90%
some abnormalities.

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:34.390 align:middle line:90%
She was in good health.

00:02:34.390 --> 00:02:37.020 align:middle line:84%
