confronted with doctors

00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:39.540 align:middle line:90%
and the fear of cancer.

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:42.660 align:middle line:84%
Our lives were
turned upside down.

00:02:42.660 --> 00:02:46.020 align:middle line:84%
