from incertitude in the breast

00:02:46.020 --> 00:02:48.330 align:middle line:90%
cancer screening discourse.

00:02:48.330 --> 00:02:51.870 align:middle line:84%
And I followed the stories of
four other women who were also

00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:53.880 align:middle line:90%
