received some worrying news.

00:02:58.230 --> 00:03:01.520 align:middle line:90%
She needs to make a decision.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:03.980 align:middle line:84%
Faced with the same
dilemma over in Canada,

00:03:03.980 --> 00:03:08.150 align:middle line:90%
Patricia made a radical choice.

00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:11.750 align:middle line:84%
Miriam underwent the same
