00:05:39.910 --> 00:05:42.946 align:middle line:90%
which need to be monitored.

00:05:42.946 --> 00:05:45.590 align:middle line:84%
ACR 4 means a
suspicion of cancer.

00:05:45.590 --> 00:05:49.337 align:middle line:90%


00:05:49.337 --> 00:05:55.366 align:middle line:84%
ACR 5, there is no doubt
over the diagnosis.

00:05:55.366 --> 00:05:56.360 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.860 align:middle line:84%
>>INTERPRETER: By comparison
with the right-hand side, which

00:05:58.860 --> 00:06:02.370 align:middle line:84%
