00:09:17.308 --> 00:09:19.180 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:09:19.180 --> 00:09:21.287 align:middle line:84%
>>INTERPRETER: There's
nothing to worry about.

00:09:21.287 --> 00:09:22.120 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.287 align:middle line:84%
>>INTERPRETER: There's
