00:27:44.530 --> 00:27:46.930 align:middle line:90%
They just deal with statistics.

00:27:46.930 --> 00:27:48.960 align:middle line:84%
In 2005, Philip
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:51.310 align:middle line:84%
