00:28:40.360 --> 00:28:44.295 align:middle line:90%


00:28:44.295 --> 00:28:45.670 align:middle line:84%
But when Philip
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

00:28:45.670 --> 00:28:48.730 align:middle line:84%
studied the rate of cases
of advanced breast cancer,

00:28:48.730 --> 00:28:53.090 align:middle line:84%
