00:29:12.280 --> 00:29:14.170 align:middle line:90%
screening and mammograms?

00:29:14.170 --> 00:29:15.820 align:middle line:90%
What does it actually achieve?

00:29:15.820 --> 00:29:20.380 align:middle line:90%


00:29:20.380 --> 00:29:22.640 align:middle line:84%
>> The doctor's initial
convictions collapsed

00:29:22.640 --> 00:29:23.780 align:middle line:90%
in the face of the data.

00:29:23.780 --> 00:29:27.490 align:middle line:90%


00:29:27.490 --> 00:29:29.860 align:middle line:84%
In France, another
epidemiologist,

00:29:29.860 --> 00:29:33.580 align:middle line:84%
